<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.6.10">
<l>uṉṉittu maṟṟoru teyvan toḻā ḷavaṉaiyallā</l>
<l>ṉummiccai colli ṉuntōḷ kulaikkappaṭu maṉṉaimīr</l>
<l>maṉṉappaṭu maṟaivā ṇaṉaivaṇ ṭuvarāpati</l>
<l>maṉṉaṉai yēttumi ṉēttu taluntoḻu tāṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Just meditating she won’t worship any god but him,</l>
<l>even though you say what you wish, o mothers whose shoulders are shaken.</l>
<l>As soon as you praise intensely the king of liberal Dhvārakā,</l>
<l>proficient in the permanent Vedas, she will dance in worship.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
